ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS (VISA EXEMPTION REQUIREMENTS FOR LITHUANIA AND POLAND) by specifying that, as of January 1, 2009, will require citizens of LITHUANIA or POLAND to possess an electronic passport to travel to Canada without a visa in an effort to guard against abuse of older passports.
